name: TCAT10
0:
”Alexa, get the next 4 stops from TCAT 10.”
”Alexa, get the next stop from TCAT 10.”
”Alexa, ask TCAT 10 when the next 2 stops are.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: t. cat ten
des: An easy way to find out when the next Route 10 buses leave Seneca station. You can either ask for the next stop, or the next 1 to 5 stops. Just ask the TCAT 10 skill when the next stop is, or ask it when the next 1-5 stops are.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
